00:10:31,130 --> 00:10:33,591
Terutama jika kau ingin perbaiki hubungan.

125
00:10:33,674 --> 00:10:36,469
Dia mungkin takkan muncul
jika tahu aku di sini.

126
00:10:37,303 --> 00:10:39,597
Ayolah, Danny. Bantulah aku.

127
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:44,352
