00:13:09,079 --> 00:13:10,706
Kenapa kau mengintai toko Choi?

154
00:13:12,374 --> 00:13:14,043
Kau kenal Frank Choi?

155
00:13:14,793 --> 00:13:18,672
Aku dan kelompokku datangi
tempat tak beralarm pada malam hari.

156
00:13:18,756 --> 00:13:21,050
Mencari makanan, recehan, semacamnya.

157
00:13:22,468 --> 00:13:25,679
Kadang Frank menangkap kami,
mengomeli kami.

158
00:13:26,472 --> 00:13:28,516
Dia takkan suka
jika kau menginjak takhtanya.

159
00:13:29,183 --> 00:13:31,227
- Benda ini?
- Ya?

160
00:13:31,519 --> 00:13:33,479
Dia juga marah jika kursi itu dipandangi.

161
00:13:34,063 --> 00:13:36,398
Katanya di situ tempatnya berpikir.

162
00:13:42,863 --> 00:13:44,490
Separuh dari apa pun itu, milikku.

163
