Pria itu sudah mati atau akan mati.

216
00:17:48,233 --> 00:17:49,485
Kenapa bilang begitu?

217
00:17:49,777 --> 00:17:51,195
Pengadu akan dihukum.

218
00:17:51,945 --> 00:17:54,239
Menurutmu dia ditahan polisi?

219
00:17:56,241 --> 00:17:58,660
